@node Requirements
@prev Requirements
@next Requirements
@{FG Highlight}Requrements@{FG Text}
-----------
DiskOptimizer needs OS 2.04 (V37) and gtlayout.library V10 to run.

@{FG Highlight}Installation@{FG Text}
------------
No special Installtion is required, simply copy DiskOptimizer to
any directory you like.
@endnode

